 rampages.<br><br>In Fear there are no walls really so you need to get all melee to circle your mob to keep him from moving.<br><br>On some casters its better to keep them moving as much as possible to disrupt their casting.. a tactic that I have been thinking about in HOT to reduce gating.<br><br>That is just a quick view of several diffrent mob placements. Our raid leader needs to look at the situation and decide what is the best strategy to use at the time then all guildies need to follow it.  When we can follow the best placement with full cooperation within the guild then we will be able to take out stuff much higher then before with less people.<br clear=all></i><br></td></tr><tr><td>
